      "content": "wait sorry i think u got mixed up. you said \"find the relative major from Eb major\" but then you explained how to find the relative minor. i actually wanted to know how to find the relative major of a minor key using the circle. like if i start at c minor, how do i use the circle to get back to eb major? and also what's this about goblins? i'm just trying to study music theory lol",
